<item>
            <title>[LU-9520] Variable buffer size in llapi changelog reader</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9520</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;LLAPI uses a fixed-sized (4096 bytes) buffer to read changelog records. It should be possible for users to set a different value.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="46141">LU-9520</key>
            <summary>Variable buffer size in llapi changelog reader</summary>
